### Double Install Snippet with Inline Embed - Default Namespace (JavaScript)

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/packages/embeds/embed-core/index.html

This function shows how to double-install the Cal.com snippet and embed an inline element using the default initialization. It ensures the embed is correctly set up even if the script was previously initialized.

```javascript
function doubleInstallSnippetWithInlineEmbed(selector) {
  Cal("init", {
    debug: true,
    calOrigin: window.calOrigin,
  });
  Cal("inline", {
    elementOrSelector: selector,
    calLink: "pro?case=doubleInstallSnippetWithInlineEmbed",
    config: {
      "flag.coep": "true"
    }
  });
  embedSnippet();
  Cal("init", {
    debug: true,
    calOrigin: window.calOrigin,
  });
  Cal("inline", {
    elementOrSelector: selector,
    calLink: "pro",
    config: {
      "flag.coep": "true"
    }
  });
}
```

