### Cal.com Embed Message Format - JavaScript

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/packages/embeds/LIFECYCLE.md

Defines the message format used for communication between the parent page and the Cal.com embed iframe. It includes a standard originator identifier 'CAL' and distinguishes between commands sent to the iframe and events received from it. This format is crucial for establishing the embed handshake and passing data.

```javascript
// Parent → Iframe (Commands)
{ originator: "CAL", method: "ui", arg: { theme: "dark" } }

// Iframe → Parent (Events)
{ originator: "CAL", type: "__iframeReady", data: { isPrerendering: false } }
```

