### Cal.com Embed Command Queuing Logic

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/packages/embeds/LIFECYCLE.md

Illustrates the process of queuing commands when the iframe is not ready and flushing them once the iframe becomes ready via `postMessage`. This ensures commands are executed in the correct order.

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[doInIframe(cmd)] --> B{iframeReady?}
    B -- No --> C[Push to queue (iframeDoQueue)]
    B -- Yes --> D[postMessage to iframe]
    C --> E[On __iframeReady event]
    E --> F[Flush queue: forEach → postMessage]
    F --> G[Clear queue]
    D --> G
```

